data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story ranch nestled in Ladson's sought-after Briddleford Ridge subdivision. Strategically positioned near Stratford High School, Goose Creek, Carnes Crossroads and I-26, this 3-bed, 2-bath gem is designed for comfort and convenience. The well-maintained residence boasts new laminate flooring, excluding two carpeted bedrooms, and with the potential to add a fourth bedroom. Step outside to enjoy the wooden deck, new shed, and private parking for 4 cars on this corner lot. With no HOA, this versatile property invites you to make it your own.
